Detailed Description

cvmx_psm_grp_mask#

These registers define membership of MHABs/MDABs within each of six groups. Along with the PSM_GRP_CDT() registers, these registers can be used to load balance jobs across many homogenous MHABs/MDABs.

Under normal circumstances, the six groups should be programmed to match the six GHBs containing the 18 MDABs and ensure MDAB jobs are balanced across GHBs.
